(164, 29, 'facts', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\"} -->\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Bishopgate Gardens are new apartments for sale in Preston city center, UK. Bishopgate Gardens offers modern &amp; superior residences in the heart of Preston city.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --> <!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\"} -->\r\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Bishopgate Gardens has a choice of one, two and three-bedroom homes with exceptional communal spaces &amp; retail units on the ground floor for utmost convenience.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->'),
